    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical and cosmetic form. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential, providing linear acceleration and a 7,900 RPM redline. The chassis has undergone a preventative subframe reinforcement to maintain structural torsional rigidity. Suspension components remain true to factory geometry with no bushing deflection, offering the communicative steering feedback characteristic of the M-division. This is a zero-fault, collector-quality example with a documented service history and flawless paint depth.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
