    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle looks and feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is deep and lustrous, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, protected by a ceramic coating that highlights its factory-fresh brilliance. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats remain supple with no visible wear to the bolsters, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a truly flawless example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
