    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This specimen has been curated with the utmost attention to detail, manifesting in a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Beyond its aesthetic perfection, the vehicle has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure its mechanical integrity aligns with its pristine appearance. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning driver who demands uncompromising quality and peerless performance. Documentation of its meticulous service history is available upon request.",
