    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and still has that new car smell! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
